title: WALK 2 River__POOL/Gym__24hr Concierge__2 RSVP Park__WOOD & Granite
posting_body: ["Welcome to the Shore, one of the Rainey District's first luxury condominium projects", 'Make this penthouse level unit (with unobstructed south-facing views of the lake) your new home', "Unit 2207 sits high above Rainey St with dual pane windows throughout: it's very quiet inside", 'Freshly painted, the kitchen and bathroom cabinets are redone including new hardware', 'Carpets in the bedrooms are relatively new but are also being steam cleaned', 'All of the blinds in the unit are motorized and the unit boasts 12ft high ceilings', 'Conveys w/ 2 parking spaces on the first level of the parking garage', 'Private/secure large storage unit on parking level 5 for an additional $200/', 'mo', '100sf of private outdoor balcony space with gorgeous views of Lady Bird Lake', 'Renovated its Lobby, expanding the package room, updated Concierge & all new furniture/decor', 'The fitness center just received new fitness equipment', 'Pool deck has all new furniture, landscaping and barbecue cook station', "It's a great time to get in at the Shore as the building is shining brighter than ever", 'Steps from the entertainment along Rainey St and the Lady Bird Lake Hike & Bike Trail!', '* I’m Clayton Holsey, a full-time Realtor with Austin Real Pros.', '*', 'This home is real and so am I!', '* Call for more info on this home or a custom list tailored specifically to your needs.', 'Clayton Holsey, REALTOR –', 'show contact info', 'Austin Real Pros has made every effort to obtain the information regarding these listings from sources deemed reliable.', ' However, we cannot warrant the complete accuracy thereof subject to errors, omissions, change of price, rental or other conditions, lease or financing, or withdrawal without notice.']
